column5: I did a tiny insidereverse short strangle now in DBX expiring tomorrow I had covered my strike23 c earlier at a nickel for gains The 22½ p is in the money and I dont look much forward to owning the stock long The 22½ c only fetches a dime right now not enough visàvis risk Shorted the strike22 c for 40 I dont go red until past 2278 or 2177 by tomorrow night if I have that math right at those prices Id let the ITM side assign anyway and write against it for next weekI did this two other times this month and it worked One day it wont work but thats how trading isAlso got out of my Jun22 long p for just better n be
